  <!-- EN: colonist died -->
  <KnowColonistDied.stages.colonist_died.label>مات مستعمر</KnowColonistDied.stages.colonist_died.label>
  <!-- EN: One of our people died. We should be able to take care of our people. -->
  <KnowColonistDied.stages.colonist_died.description>توفي أحد أفراد شعبنا. يجب أن نكون قادرين على رعاية شعبنا.</KnowColonistDied.stages.colonist_died.description>
  
  <!-- Thought_Memory, null. Label: {PAWN}. LabelSocial: {PAWN}. Description: {PAWN} -->
  <!-- EN: justified execution of colonist -->
  <KnowColonistExecuted.stages.justified_execution_of_colonist.label>إعدام مبرر لمستعمر</KnowColonistExecuted.stages.justified_execution_of_colonist.label>
  <!-- EN: A guilty colonist was executed. It was justified, but still sad. -->
  <KnowColonistExecuted.stages.justified_execution_of_colonist.description>تم إعدام مستعمر مذنب. كان مبررًا، لكنه لا يزال محزنًا.</KnowColonistExecuted.stages.justified_execution_of_colonist.description>
  <!-- EN: colonist euthanized -->
  <KnowColonistExecuted.stages.colonist_euthanized.label>تم قتل مستعمر رحيمًا</KnowColonistExecuted.stages.colonist_euthanized.label>
  <!-- EN: A colonist was euthanized. It was humane, but still sad. -->
  <KnowColonistExecuted.stages.colonist_euthanized.description>تم القتل الرحيم لمستعمر. كان إنسانيًا، لكنه لا يزال محزنًا.</KnowColonistExecuted.stages.colonist_euthanized.description>
  <!-- EN: colonist executed -->
  <KnowColonistExecuted.stages.colonist_executed.label>إعدام مستعمر</KnowColonistExecuted.stages.colonist_executed.label>
  <!-- EN: A colonist was killed in cold blood. It seemed a bit evil. -->
  <KnowColonistExecuted.stages.colonist_executed.description>قُتل مستعمر بدم بارد. بدا شريرًا بعض الشيء.</KnowColonistExecuted.stages.colonist_executed.description>
  <!-- EN: colonist organ-harvested -->
  <KnowColonistExecuted.stages.colonist_organharvested.label>مستعمر تم حصاد أعضائه</KnowColonistExecuted.stages.colonist_organharvested.label>
  <!-- EN: A colonist died because someone took body parts from them. It's horrible. -->
  <KnowColonistExecuted.stages.colonist_organharvested.description>توفي مستعمر لأن أحدهم أخذ أجزاء من جسده. إنه أمر مروع.</KnowColonistExecuted.stages.colonist_organharvested.description>
  <!-- EN: colonist ripscanned -->
  <KnowColonistExecuted.stages.colonist_ripscanned.label>مستعمر تم مسحه ضوئيًا مميتًا</KnowColonistExecuted.stages.colonist_ripscanned.label>
  <!-- EN: A colonist died in our ripscanner. Their brain was burned up to feed the machine. It's horrible. -->
  <KnowColonistExecuted.stages.colonist_ripscanned.description>توفي مستعمر في الماسح الضوئي المميت. تم حرق دماغه لتغذية الآلة. إنه أمر مروع.</KnowColonistExecuted.stages.colonist_ripscanned.description>
  
