  <!-- Thought_Memory, null. Label: {0}(otherPawn.LabelShort), {1}(otherPawn). LabelSocial: {PAWN}, {OTHERPAWN}. Description: {PAWN}, {OTHERPAWN} -->
  <!-- EN: innocent prisoner died -->
  <KnowPrisonerDiedInnocent.stages.innocent_prisoner_died.label>مات سجين بريء</KnowPrisonerDiedInnocent.stages.innocent_prisoner_died.label>
  <!-- EN: One of our prisoners died despite being harmless. We should be able to take care of our prisoners. If we wanted them dead, we could have at least conducted an orderly execution rather than permit that barbarism. -->
  <KnowPrisonerDiedInnocent.stages.innocent_prisoner_died.description>توفي أحد سجناءنا رغم أنه غير مؤذٍ. يجب أن نكون قادرين على رعاية سجناءنا. إذا أردناهم موتى، كان بإمكاننا على الأقل إجراء إعدام منظم بدلاً من السماح بتلك الهمجية.</KnowPrisonerDiedInnocent.stages.innocent_prisoner_died.description>
  
